Dialogue: 0,0:00:-12.-27,0:00:-10.-26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-10.-24,0:00:-08.-36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger,\Nthe King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-08.-34,0:00:-06.-05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-06.-03,0:00:-02.-18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before\Nhis death drove people to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-02.-16,0:00:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure?\NIf you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.67,0:00:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.85,0:00:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men head for the\NGrand Line in pursuit of their dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.59,0:00:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly\Nentered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.49,0:00:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.86,0:00:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.77,0:00:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.97,0:00:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.61,0:00:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever,\NI take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it's not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.46,0:01:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.17,0:01:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard\Nsomeone else's biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.47,0:01:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn't there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.14,0:01:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.65,0:01:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.36,0:01:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand do you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.60,0:01:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.97,0:01:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.09,0:02:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, girlie?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.00,0:02:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want me to return\Nthe village that badly?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.07,0:02:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how's this?\NLet's make an agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.44,0:02:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agreement?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.88,0:02:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.11,0:02:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gather up 100 million\NBerries and bring it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.12,0:02:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do so and I'll let the village\Ngo and give you freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.45,0:02:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Honest?!\N--Honest!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.29,0:02:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd die before I break an\Nagreement concerning money.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.69,0:02:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter how\Nmany years it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.60,0:02:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll honor our agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.97,0:02:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I absolutely will save up\N100 million Berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.41,0:02:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellemere-san! I will do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.78,0:02:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much time it takes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.98,0:03:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Luffy Rises!\NResult of the Broken Promise!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.76,0:03:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen-san? And the navy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.00,0:03:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the girl thief known as Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.61,0:03:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our information has it you've hidden\Ntreasure you stole from pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.35,0:03:35.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The government hereby confiscates\Nall the property you have stolen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.36,0:03:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?\NDid you not hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.63,0:03:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The government\Nhereby takes possession
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.63,0:03:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of everything you\Nstole from the pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.70,0:03:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my. You're very passionate\Nabout your duties, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.71,0:03:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not brave enough\Nto stand up to pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.51,0:03:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you deal with sneak thieves\Ninstead to earn brownie points.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.81,0:04:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about superb!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.82,0:04:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's a warning for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.82,0:04:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a leader of the Arlong Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.99,0:04:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mess with me, and Arlong\Nwon't sit by quietly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.32,0:04:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silly girl. Do you think you're\Ndealing with me on equal footing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.60,0:04:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find the stolen goods!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.17,0:04:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.64,0:04:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.91,0:04:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what the navy\Nshould be doing right now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.12,0:04:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Arlong Pirates have killed people,\Nand even destroyed towns!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.59,0:04:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.46,0:04:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's ruling over this island and\Ntrampling all over people's lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.33,0:04:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is ignoring that major problem
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.96,0:04:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and raking in stolen goods from a thief
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.30,0:04:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what the government stands for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.07,0:04:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk all big.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.40,0:04:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Continue your search!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.84,0:05:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People all over the island've been\Nwaiting for your help for years now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.81,0:05:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you just pass\Nthem by and come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.28,0:05:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Colonel! This tangerine\Norchard seems suspicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.08,0:05:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dig it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.92,0:05:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your filthy hands off of\NBellemere-san's tangerine orchard!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.76,0:05:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you have my money!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.29,0:05:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That money's for...\NThat money's for...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.60,0:05:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This girl's money is meant\Nto save Cocoyashi Village!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.64,0:05:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What gives you the right\Nto take it away, navy man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.98,0:05:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? A lowly village representative,\Ntalking down to a navy colonel?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.35,0:05:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen-san... How do you know about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.09,0:05:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always known, Nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.56,0:05:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm... joining...\N--Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.56,0:06:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm joining... the Arlong Pirates...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.57,0:06:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.07,0:06:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.17,0:06:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.57,0:06:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't believe\Nwhat you'd done then,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.81,0:06:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I confronted Nojiko later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.98,0:06:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone in the village\Nhas known since then
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.41,0:06:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that you stayed with the Arlong\NPirates so you could save the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.32,0:06:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we pretended we didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.25,0:06:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because our hopes would keep you\Nfrom running away from Arlong
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.09,0:06:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if you ever decided to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.93,0:06:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.20,0:06:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.27,0:06:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying all the\Nvillagers are thieves,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.50,0:06:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and we should arrest them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.77,0:06:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's saying that each and every\None of us is fighting to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.81,0:06:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But only because we can't rely\Non any of you government people!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.15,0:06:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not gonna save our village,\Nthen get the hell out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.39,0:06:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dilly-dally and Arlong'll\Ngo after your ship, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.59,0:07:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Arlong will?\NI wouldn't be so sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.70,0:07:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still haven't found it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.27,0:07:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're looking for 100 million\NBerries here! Not a grain of rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.14,0:07:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you! How do you\Nknow how much there is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.94,0:07:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the 100 million?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.98,0:07:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just got the feeling\Nthere's that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.26,0:07:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me he...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.23,0:07:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me Arlong sent you here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.80,0:07:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.50,0:07:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're simply dealing with theft\Nas any government workers would.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.04,0:07:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What rotten scum!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.38,0:07:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe the navy would\Nstoop to being pirate cronies!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.48,0:08:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arlong!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.25,0:08:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.20,0:08:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.63,0:08:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed you could\Ngather this much, girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.34,0:08:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all ragged and stained with blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.57,0:08:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter! Money is money!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.81,0:08:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thirty percent of this is all mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.65,0:08:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.91,0:08:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch that... Don't touch that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.95,0:08:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.75,0:08:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch that... Don't touch that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.22,0:08:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.57,0:09:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.21,0:09:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nojiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.78,0:09:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nojiko!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.82,0:09:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pinwheel, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.53,0:09:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, that was so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.57,0:09:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought up a good move!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.24,0:09:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor! Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.64,0:09:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Gen-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.48,0:09:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Nojiko's been shot!\N--By who?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.11,0:09:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--The navy!\N--The navy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.58,0:09:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nojiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.12,0:09:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.92,0:09:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arlong's been working with the navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.26,0:09:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.49,0:09:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's lied to Nami\Nfor the last eight years.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.23,0:09:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He never intended to\Nhonor their agreement!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.76,0:09:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?!\N--Oh, no! Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.60,0:09:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard!\NHe lied to our Nacchan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.24,0:10:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nacchan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.57,0:10:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.84,0:10:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heya, Nami! What's up?\NNeed help with anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.58,0:10:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.05,0:10:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This has nothing to do with you!\NLeave the damn island already!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arlong... Arlong...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.70,0:10:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arlong!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.03,0:10:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd die before I break an\Nagreement concerning money.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.21,0:10:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter how\Nmany years it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.41,0:10:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll honor our agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.91,0:10:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arlong!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.95,0:10:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's her problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arlong!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.44,0:11:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? What's wrong,\Nskilled surveyor of ours?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.04,0:11:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the angry look?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.01,0:11:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The navy men you have under\Nyour control stole all my money!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.65,0:11:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to dying before\Nbreaking promises about money?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.02,0:11:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.46,0:11:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did I break our promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.19,0:11:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't play dumb!\NYou teamed up with the navy to--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.33,0:11:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did I break our\Npromise? Let's hear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.28,0:11:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you... Damn you! Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.98,0:11:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see! So your money's been stolen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.98,0:11:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.52,0:11:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But an agreement is an agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.86,0:12:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't gather up\N100 million Berries for me to see,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.86,0:12:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid I can't give\Nyou the village back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.43,0:12:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scum!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.60,0:12:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only 100 million Berries!\NJust start saving up again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.48,0:12:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or are you gonna run out on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.75,0:12:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you do run away, I'll kill\Neveryone in Cocoyashi Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.46,0:12:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.72,0:12:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We pretended we didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.46,0:12:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because our hopes would keep you\Nfrom running away from Arlong
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.46,0:12:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,if you ever decided to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.41,0:12:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Finally running away, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.65,0:12:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't we chase after her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.48,0:13:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chase? What for? She won't run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.62,0:13:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She could never abandon\Nthe lives of the villagers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.16,0:13:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You certainly do know\Nhow to play dirty...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.09,0:13:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way would I let such an exceptional\Nsurveyor as Nami go so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.33,0:13:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not a heartless devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.87,0:13:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once she's done surveying\Nall of the world's seas,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.17,0:13:25.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give her her freedom!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.61,0:13:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's like decades from now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.28,0:13:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even a hundred years'd be enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.09,0:13:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Let's meet up with Luffy ASAP!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.33,0:13:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sanji. What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Appreciating happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.36,0:13:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.23,0:13:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san's lived with many times\Nthe suffering of a normal person.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.71,0:13:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to take away\Nthat suffering of hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.38,0:14:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there any happiness\Ngreater than this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.08,0:14:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your ulterior motive's\Nway obvious, Love Cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.09,0:14:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fighting for a beautiful person.\NWhat's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.79,0:14:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what this is for!\NIt's for Nami and the villagers!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.73,0:14:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shaddup.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.40,0:14:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit your jabbering and let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.01,0:14:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No more of this!\NTake up your weapons!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.68,0:14:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.45,0:14:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen-san! Everyone!\NPlease! Don't be hasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.99,0:14:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't die! It'll all be over!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.23,0:14:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to survive,\Nor everything will end!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.36,0:14:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eight years ago, we swore\Nnot to throw away our lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.90,0:14:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how painful and insulting\Nit was to be ruled by them,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.94,0:15:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we swore to fight the patient fight\Nas long as Nami was cheerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.98,0:15:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is their answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.01,0:15:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that our village's chance for\Nfreedom is gone, we have no hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.68,0:15:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More than that,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.05,0:15:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we must make those fishmen pay\Nfor toying with that girl's kindness!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.42,0:15:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any objections?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.86,0:15:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.39,0:15:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were always fully ready\Nto fight at any time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.66,0:15:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse to let them\Nrule over me any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.20,0:15:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.04,0:15:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.68,0:15:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little more!\NJust wait a little more!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.81,0:15:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll work hard again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.88,0:15:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll save up the money again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.55,0:15:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be easy this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.39,0:15:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm used to it! I'll be fine!\NThere's no need to worry at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.22,0:15:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothing\Ncompared to back then!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.06,0:16:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, no more dying!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.40,0:16:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone! I'm fine! I'm just fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.98,0:16:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can stop now... Even you\Nknow there's no point now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.38,0:16:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fought very well, carrying our\Nlives on your back all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.95,0:16:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Joining them must've been\Neven more painful for you
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.29,0:16:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,than being cut through the heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.96,0:16:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You fought very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.70,0:16:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.20,0:16:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the village now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.94,0:16:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gen-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.61,0:16:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it, Nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.14,0:16:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.28,0:16:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Nacchan...\N--Nami...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.48,0:16:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're crafty, and you have a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.05,0:16:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nojiko! Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.86,0:17:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.39,0:17:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.96,0:17:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to see anyone\Nelse get hurt by them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.40,0:17:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll die, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.60,0:17:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.91,0:17:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use!\NWe've made up our minds!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.98,0:17:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of our way, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.99,0:17:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.46,0:17:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we can't win, let's\Nshow 'em what we're made of!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.86,0:18:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arlong!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.13,0:18:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arlong! Arlong!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.34,0:18:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arlong! Arlong!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.61,0:18:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arlong! Arlong! Arlong!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.38,0:18:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arlong! Arlong!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.98,0:18:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arl--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.85,0:18:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.09,0:18:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?!\NYou don't even know anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.60,0:18:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't even know what's happened\Non this island the past 8 years!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.37,0:18:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.47,0:18:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This has nothing to do with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.97,0:18:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, leave the\Ndamn island already!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.71,0:18:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. You told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.58,0:19:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave! I don't need you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.11,0:19:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave! Leave! Leave! Leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.68,0:19:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave! Leave! Leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.22,0:19:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.17,0:19:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.84,0:19:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.63,0:19:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.07,0:19:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch my treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.40,0:20:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.45,0:20:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.78,0:20:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.22,0:20:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Are you guys alright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.02,0:20:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Arlong do this to you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.53,0:20:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.96,0:20:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have business with the fishmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.03,0:20:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that we know the\Ntruth about Big Sis Nami,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.77,0:20:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we felt the only thing\Nwe can do was defeat Arlong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.47,0:20:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we challenged him...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.14,0:20:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we lost by a hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.48,0:20:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but we're not letting\Nyou through this door,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.15,0:20:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,seeing as you have no hope for victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.98,0:20:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.09,0:20:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're waiting for certain\Nmen to arrive here, you see!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.72,0:20:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Certain men?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.66,0:21:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd bet my life on it. They will come!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.31,0:21:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.23,0:21:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's them...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.43,0:21:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.77,0:21:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they can't handle them,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.37,0:21:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then there's no hope\Nfor not only this island,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.64,0:21:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but for the future of\Nthe entire East Blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.87,0:21:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The faces of those four men\Nwho're here to change destiny...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.28,0:21:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Burn their images into your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.82,0:22:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.00,0:22:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you think those two\Nidiots were part of Zoro's group?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.07,0:22:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro's? They seemed too weak for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.91,0:22:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not even worth killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.47,0:22:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.89,0:22:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.99,0:22:42.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one of you is Arlong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.07,0:22:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My overflowing feelings don't connect
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.07,0:22:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as I firmly squeeze your hand back
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.98,0:22:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll set off by myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.91,0:23:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so keep watching me intently\Nas I go into the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.76,0:23:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking about it\Na bit since this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.76,0:23:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it so hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.33,0:23:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting from some point, I haven't\Nbeen able to get away from that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.81,0:23:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to catch those\Nfeelings that rushed off,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.68,0:23:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm already about\Nto overtake myself, even
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.56,0:23:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to embrace my\Ndreams that have jumped out
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.56,0:23:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With you, I can run there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.57,0:23:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just had to run ahead by yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.14,0:24:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said don't hog all the prey!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.54,0:24:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.51,0:24:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Huh?\N--What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.65,0:24:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's the thing!\NI'm kind of in trouble! Hear me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.95,0:24:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, crap! That guy\Nplans to do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.62,0:24:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do?\NWhat do I do?! What do I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.09,0:24:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.42,0:24:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.66,0:24:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Luffy in Big Trouble!\NFishmen vs. the Luffy Pirates"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.89,0:24:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
